      <!-- Class Manipulation Section  -->
      <h3 class = "mainTopic"> Class Manipulation  </h3>
      <p> Being able to add a class allows for changes or updates to the styling of an HTML page much easier. Let's walk through an example. </p>

      <ul>
        <li><Strong>addClass()</Strong>

